These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bike, skateboard
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, fisherman, pilot
House: ranch-style, craftsman, modern
3 different games are played: domino, backgammon, whist
1. the person driving the bike is between the lawyer and the person playing domino##2
2. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing domino##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the fisherman##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the modern house##1
6. the lawyer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Transport          | airplane      | bike        | skateboard     |
| Job         | pilot | fisherman | lawyer    |
| House   | craftsman   | ranch-style       | modern |
| Game         | domino  | backgammon      | whist    |

