.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, dancing, video-games
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, coffee
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, chestnut, aquamarine
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, poppy, dahlia
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person drinking juice is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
7. the person who growsdahlia is between the person drinking juice and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Hobby           | dancing    | video-games | woodworking |
| Beverage   | juice | lemonade       | coffee   |
| Color           | aquamarine  | chestnut   | light-blue     |
| Flower         | poppy | dahlia       | iris   |

