.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, lawyer, photographer
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, october, december
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, bellflower, tulip
3 different games are played: monopoly, chess, domino
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the photographer is the person playing domino##1
3. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
4. the accountant is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person playing domino##2
5. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4
6. the person who growstulip is the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Job          | photographer | accountant | lawyer |
| Birthday   | december     | november | october |
| Flower           | bellflower       | balloon-flower   | tulip    |
| Game     | domino      | monopoly   | chess |

