.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
City: rome, san-francisco, hamburg
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, 7up
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, house, classical
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, bellflower, azalea
1. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the person drinking 7up is the fan of house##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
7. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| City         | san-francisco  | rome       | hamburg |
| Beverage           | 7up     | fanta      | almond-milk   |
| Music-Genre   | house | ambient | classical     |
| Flower   | amaryllis      | azalea   | bellflower     |

