.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, cricket, volleyball
3 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, cat
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, writing, rock-climbing
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, brown, grey
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
6. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
7. the person who likes grey is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Sport      | volleyball     | cricket   | ice-hockey         |
| Pet           | goat | goldfish | cat |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing      | writing   | collecting            |
| Color   | brown   | grey  | mauve         |

