There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, mirinda
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
2. the japanese is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the engineer is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the pilot is on the left or right of the dancer##3
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the dancer##1
6. the argentine is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
7. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Sport          | volleyball | snowboarding | soccer |
| Job   | pilot  | dancer    | engineer |
| Nationality   | japanese  | argentine   | turkish    |
| Beverage     | mirinda   | coffee       | almond-milk |

