3. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the person who likes red is on the left of the wooden house##1
6. the person who likes black is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the wooden house and the person who likes azure##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
