3. the person driving the ship is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
