3. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person playing go is the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the victorian house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
6. the person eating peach is in an odd position##4
7. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
