.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-11::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, black, azure
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, funk, dubstep
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, prince, oliveros
3 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, pony
1. the fan of funk is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of funk is the siglo-smoker##1
3. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes black##1
4. the person who likes azure is in an odd position##4
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
6. the fan of soul is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the fan of dubstep is the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3       |
| Color      | azure     | black      | emerald  |
| Music-Genre          | funk     | dubstep | soul       |
| Cigar   | siglo  | oliveros    | prince      |
| Pet         | pony | mouse  | ferret |

