.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, strawberry, pomegranate
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, country, jazz
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, april, november
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, nigerian
1. the nigerian is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
4. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the malaysian##1
6. the fan of punk is on the left of the nigerian##1
7. the person eating strawberry is between the person eating cabbage and the person who's birthday is in january##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food      | pomegranate       | strawberry   | cabbage |
| Music-Genre   | punk | jazz     | country |
| Birthday           | january      | april | november    |
| Nationality         | malaysian  | nigerian     | canadian |

