3. the person traveling to marseilles is in an even position##4
4. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
5. the tower house is the person who likes lavender##1
6. the person who growsazalea is in the middle##1
7. the person who likes red is on the far left##1
8. the modern house is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
9. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| City           | venice | marseilles   | boston |
| Flower   | bellflower  | azalea    | zinnia    |
| House         | modern    | tower | cottage   |
| Color     | red  | lavender     | aquamarine  |

