The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, boat, snowmobile
1. the owner of the hamster is the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the boat is between the bolivar-smoker and the person watching satire movies##2
5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| Movie-Genre         | romance    | animation   | satire      |
| Cigar           | bolivar | old-henry    | pall-mall |
| Pet   | hamster       | rabbit | dog      |
| Transport         | snowmobile         | boat   | skateboard     |

