The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, video-games, skydiving
House: farmhouse, tower, cape-cod
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, april, february
1. the person who likes green is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is the tower house##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
7. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3      |
| Color          | coral     | green   | yellow     |
| Hobby   | skydiving   | video-games   | traveling      |
| House   | tower | farmhouse | cape-cod    |
| Birthday     | february  | july   | april |

