City: hamburg, miami, liverpool
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, emerald, light-blue
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, siglo, prince
1. the siglo-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
3. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the prince-smoker is the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person who likes light-blue is in an even position##4
6. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who likes emerald##1
7. the person who likes red is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person drinking mirinda is the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| Beverage          | mirinda  | iced-tea   | sprite |
| City   | miami      | liverpool      | hamburg   |
| Color   | red     | light-blue | emerald |
| Cigar         | siglo | montecristo   | prince   |

