.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different games are played: bridge, whist, canasta
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, drawing, skydiving
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, aconite, azalea
There 3 different types of food: potato, avocado, carrot
1. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person who growsazalea is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person playing whist##1
4. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
6. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Game           | bridge  | canasta | whist   |
| Hobby   | drawing | skydiving           | hiking      |
| Flower           | azalea   | aconite          | daffodil |
| Food     | potato    | carrot           | avocado |

 